# Metricool API Configuration
# Get these from your Metricool account: Settings > API

# Your Metricool API Token (required for authentication)
VITE_METRICOOL_API_TOKEN=your_api_token_here

# Your Metricool User ID (found in Metricool settings)
VITE_METRICOOL_USER_ID=your_user_id_here

# Instructions:
# 1. Subscribe to Metricool Advanced plan ($39/mo) or Custom plan
# 2. Go to Metricool Settings > API
# 3. Copy your API Token and User ID
# 4. Create a .env file (copy this file)
# 5. Replace the placeholder values above with your actual credentials
# 6. Add each client's Metricool blogId in src/pages/ControlDashboard.tsx

# Note: Never commit your .env file to git (it's already in .gitignore)
